Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:57.58,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}天空寬廣無際
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:03.49,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}天色灰霾不散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:08.70,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}揹負命運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:14.43,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}捨身前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:19.66,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}我要將沸騰的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:25.51,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}表露於這陰天之下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:31.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}竭力守護之物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:35.63,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}正維繫著當下與未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:41.44,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}即便此刻 化作露水消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:46.59,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,500)}也請你絕不言棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:57.72,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(500,1000)}你知道 這世上並無永不終結的悲傷
